Task – Create a Stylish Contact Form
Objective:
Recreate the given contact form design exactly as shown in the reference image.
Requirements:
1.Header Section
Title: CONTACT US
Subtitle: Fill out the form below to learn more!
Background image (blurred effect optional but appreciated).
2.Form Fields
First Name (text input)
Last Name (text input)
Email (text input with required validation)
Comments (textarea)
3.Submit Button
Style it similar to the sample image (blue background, white text).
Add hover effect.
4.Layout & Styling
Center the form on the page.
Use consistent margins, and font sizes.
Form should be responsive (look good on mobile to submit button.
